pageContext.claim: “You know, where they have 100 miles of cars, where they have thousands of tractors...”
pageContext.analysis: A total fabrication. The biggest tractor parade for Trump we could find was in Ohio, with nearly 300 combines and tractors. A September tractor parade in Jefferson, Iowa registered "80 tractors and trucks." There appears to be no estimate for the parade in Atlantic, Iowa that Trump appears to be referencing but video indicates few tractors and mostly pickup trucks, numbering at best a few hundred.
